{"tid":1107311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮: 正尋求將非法移民送往大愛包容「庇護城市」","createTime":"2019-04-15T07:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T07:56:10.000Z","uid":62257,"like":85,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"296a4c838a6550fcd056d2114e31d0d4b91cd022","tid":1107311,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:01:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190415/s00005/1555288792223/白宮正尋求將非法移民送往庇護城市\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190415%2Fs00005%2F1555288792223%2F%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E6%AD%A3%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E5%B0%87%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E9%80%81%E5%BE%80%E5%BA%87%E8%AD%B7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUaj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=2c2ee6c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190415%2Fs00005%2F1555288792223%2F%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E6%AD%A3%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E5%B0%87%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E9%80%81%E5%BE%80%E5%BA%87%E8%AD%B7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82&h=b35f48f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190415/s00005/1555288792223/白宮正尋求將非法移民送往庇護城市</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190415/s00005/3087c3b9bbe37a232b0f89bc94cfa0c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190415%2Fs00005%2F3087c3b9bbe37a232b0f89bc94cfa0c1.jpg&h=f088f55a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國白宮發言人桑德斯表示，特朗普政府正尋求將非法移民送往國內的「庇護城市」。民主黨眾議院司法委員會主席認為，特朗普推動此計劃是濫用總統權力。<br />\n<br />\n「庇護城市」是不願配合聯邦政府將非法移民驅逐出境的城市，這些城市通常由民主黨執政，例如三藩市、洛杉磯和紐約。<br />\n白宮發言人桑德斯當地時間周日（14日），接受美國廣播公司（ABC）政論節目《本週》（This Week）訪問時指出，「聽到這個構想時，他頗喜歡」，又表示政府正尋找是否有可行的方案，並進行「全面、徹底且廣泛的審議」。<br />\n民主黨眾議院司法委員會主席Jerry Nadler認為，特朗普推動將非法移民轉移到「庇護城市」是「再次濫用總統權力」。特朗普則在twitter發文，堅稱美國「絕對有權把被拘捕的非法移民送往「庇護城市」。"},{"pid":"240ee9bcecdc0ec9dc648464f13f8e35af17e5a7","tid":1107311,"uid":6103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41466b39fe1187bc71768352b657ecffe100e51","tid":1107311,"uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"加州RIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b0ddf80a5f92b14809ff447612b8d1d3170ab4","tid":1107311,"uid":62257,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"e41466b39fe1187bc71768352b657ecffe100e51","tid":1107311,"uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"加州RIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:05:07.000Z","msg":"荷里活好歡迎㗎喎"},{"pid":"b048fb6368fccb1524a3ffa22e874e4f914a19ef","tid":1107311,"uid":28053,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:07:09.000Z","msg":"NewYork餐館唔需要咁多墨仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但墨仔真心勤力，收半個人人工 做兩個人嘅野..."},{"pid":"05b362e5b5d4255a70811d3150e216061d559efb","tid":1107311,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03fb15b6875522d19a0210bbd4c75843d21274e","tid":1107311,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"要班大愛人士受番難民帶黎既治安問題"},{"pid":"8a4c98759f31a61f4c1bac3bf03195e6f14e6c3f","tid":1107311,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:37:05.000Z","msg":"大愛撚快d 包容非法移民啦"},{"pid":"f1edcf3c3b47c7230191c8e2e5303f81b9890207","tid":1107311,"uid":85461,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:38:52